Edition:
Quote: Can they not discover some mode of "painless extinction," .. so that the bereaved parents, the Provincial Councilors, may not be too violently afflicted at the loss of their bantlings - as seems to be the case with the Wellington Provincials, whose last crop of laws has been dreadfully worried by those wild dogs of the General Government?
